00:16:38,200 --> 00:16:41,139
[SPEAKER_00] iako, eto, ja nisam uopće bila svjesna.

131
00:16:41,139 --> 00:16:43,659
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, to je bilo badnja misa,

132
00:16:43,659 --> 00:16:46,759
[SPEAKER_00] dvije tisućita, veliki parti, ono,

133
00:16:46,759 --> 00:16:50,440
