202
00:22:13,619 --> 00:22:17,180
[SPEAKER_00] dođem na vrata i vidim tu mladu sestru,

203
00:22:17,180 --> 00:22:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] Petru, novici Jatkinju,

204
00:22:18,519 --> 00:22:21,500
[SPEAKER_00] koja mi donijela srce, sliku,

205
00:22:21,500 --> 00:22:23,539
[SPEAKER_00] presvjetog srca Marijinog,

206
