255
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] svaki put kad bi došli u Međugorje,

256
00:23:49,019 --> 00:23:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] prije kolokvija,

257
00:23:49,940 --> 00:23:51,680
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno nakon kolokvija,

258
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:53,420
