[SPEAKER_00] gdje je gospodin se objavio

1136
01:00:03,039 --> 01:00:03,960
[SPEAKER_00] u svojoj ljubavi

1137
01:00:03,960 --> 01:00:04,900
[SPEAKER_00] i u svojoj dobroti,

1138
01:00:04,900 --> 01:00:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] jer kao što sam i nekako mislila

1139
01:00:07,400 --> 01:00:08,679
[SPEAKER_00] da ova tema već razbude,

1140
01:00:08,679 --> 01:00:11,599
[SPEAKER_00] Bog okreće na dobro

1141
01:00:11,599 --> 01:00:13,400
[SPEAKER_00] sve onima koji ga ljube.

1142
01:00:13,400 --> 01:00:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] Čistog iskrenog srca

1143
01:00:15,639 --> 01:00:17,340
[SPEAKER_00] desio se tu trenutak

1144
01:00:17,340 --> 01:00:19,360
[SPEAKER_00] kad je naš mlađi sin

1145
01:00:19,360 --> 01:00:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] jedne zime pao

1146
01:00:21,800 --> 01:00:22,980
[SPEAKER_00] sa atomskog skloništa

1147
01:00:22,980 --> 01:00:25,320
[SPEAKER_00] sa 6-7 metara visine

1148
01:00:25,320 --> 01:00:30,480
[SPEAKER_00] i ostao ležat,

1149
01:00:30,480 --> 01:00:32,059
[SPEAKER_00] nepokretan, nepomičan.

1150
01:00:32,059 --> 01:00:33,420
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam dotrčala,

1151
01:00:33,420 --> 01:00:34,800
[SPEAKER_00] došla je hitna jako brzo,

1152
01:00:34,800 --> 01:00:35,800
[SPEAKER_00] mi rekli su ne znam,

1153
01:00:35,800 --> 01:00:37,199
[SPEAKER_00] jako je visoko.

1154
01:00:37,199 --> 01:00:40,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bruno je bio u bolnici,

1155
01:00:40,360 --> 01:00:42,199
[SPEAKER_00] sve pretrage su prošli,

1156
01:00:42,199 --> 01:00:42,699
[SPEAKER_00] napravili.

1157
01:00:42,699 --> 01:00:45,119
[SPEAKER_00] Moj prvi onako instinkt

1158
01:00:45,119 --> 01:00:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] kad sam došla do njega

1159
01:00:46,199 --> 01:00:47,199
[SPEAKER_00] i vidla ga da leži

1160
01:00:47,199 --> 01:00:49,380
[SPEAKER_00] i da ne miče ni ruke ni noge,

1161
01:00:49,380 --> 01:00:50,659
[SPEAKER_00] znači možda je nepokretan,

1162
01:00:50,659 --> 01:00:51,320
[SPEAKER_00] možda je slomio kralježnicu,

1163
01:00:51,320 --> 01:00:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] kralježnicu,

1164
01:00:51,900 --> 01:00:52,679
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam pogledala nebo,

1165
01:00:52,679 --> 01:00:53,300
[SPEAKER_00] rekla sam Bože,

1166
01:00:53,300 --> 01:00:54,000
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam spremna.

1167
01:00:54,000 --> 01:00:56,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sve prihvaćam,

1168
01:00:56,079 --> 01:00:56,659
[SPEAKER_00] ja te ljubim

1169
01:00:56,659 --> 01:00:57,699
[SPEAKER_00] i samo mi daj snage

1170
01:00:57,699 --> 01:00:59,300
[SPEAKER_00] da nosim taj svoj križ.

1171
01:00:59,300 --> 01:01:01,400
[SPEAKER_00] To me upravo naučila zajednica.

1172
01:01:01,400 --> 01:01:04,159
[SPEAKER_00] Život je ljep,

1173
01:01:04,159 --> 01:01:05,920
[SPEAKER_00] ima malih križeva,

1174
01:01:05,920 --> 01:01:06,719
